" Map ø to : in normal mode
nnoremap ø :

" Map space to : in normal mode
"nnoremap Ø ?

" Map $ to ¤ in normal mode
:noremap ¤ $

" Map <escape> to jj in insert mode
map! jj <Esc>

" Map shift + space to clear highlighting
nnoremap <S-space> :noh <CR>

" map å and Å to { and [
:map å {
map! å {
:map Å [
map! Å [

" map æ and Æ to } and ]
:map æ }
map! æ }
:map Æ ]
map! Æ ]

map! Ø $
